class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae201ff08fd31c2c6186f55514d82c0a062d969","tid":595942,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"source ?"},{"pid":"9e6b61d8738b7e8b598031ecfc0ee54c33a0eaf5","tid":595942,"uid":14103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"西甲果堆都係咁架啦 點解要分主客場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  記者你去西維爾睇波人地噓貝迪斯果陣你叫佢唔好噓丫笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017d4b3dba2c01c9330b313df561813f3f886038","tid":595942,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82896337ca33612693d45f1294e1526a3cf6b49e","tid":595942,"uid":54373,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾記者第一次入場睇波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"有記者在賽後嘆道：「咁都入波？埋咗稿寫歷史第一分啦，唉。」"},{"pid":"15c33ea66c98c46598af78a406f9d266e2b689ce","tid":595942,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"好似東亞運篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff21474fe64ccdb8e725928c365f5c7e074da1bc","tid":595942,"uid":34284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:04:07.000Z","msg":"篇文咩媒體出？ 可以罷睇"},{"pid":"9259727e367b354927becb99160302885689e45b","tid":595942,"uid":94241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"on9 記者 第一次睇波 邊間垃圾請埋d垃圾記者"},{"pid":"c1b6eaf805f1673ca89e70c34269798251079647","tid":595942,"uid":9710,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:05:13.000Z","msg":"香港特色的東亞運動會<br />\n左一句「踢出傳奇」，右一句「創造神話」；全城忽爾愛港，高叫「We are Hong Kong」! 據報，一場精彩的球賽，一隊充滿希望的生力軍，「把港人團結起來」； 就是連黑臉特首也在失控地喝采！只是，歡呼聲以外，球場上還有那「萬眾一心」的喝倒采聲。作為東道主，港人贏了金牌，輸了風度； 創出傳奇一刻，欠缺體育精神！<br />\n<br />\n報載，每當足球傳到日本球員腳尖上，全場港隊擁躉即報以噓聲─「日本守門員準備開出龍門球，他們噓；日本球員